Brian Molefe gained infamy when he claimed he was visiting a Saxonwold shebeen when quizzed about his relationships with the Guptas. JOHANNESBURG - Former Transnet CEO, Brian Molefe, has admitted having a close relationship with the Gupta family. Molefe gained infamy when he claimed he was visiting a Saxonwold shebeen when quizzed about his relationships with the Guptas. But Molefe does, however, deny knowing Gupta lieutenant, Salim Essa. READ: Police should protect witnesses: Zondo Molefe was testifying at the state capture inquiry on Monday. eNCA's Khayelihle Khumalo shares more details in the video above.